<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<body style="background-color: #333333">
    <h1 style="color: #FFFFFF; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Verify Email Address</h1>
    <p style="color: #AEAEAE; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">
        Thank you for creating a new account at NAME. Click the link below to
        verify that this email address belongs to your account.
    </p>

    <p style="color: #c07b7b; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">
        If you did not create an account with us you can ignore this
        message.
    </p>

    <a style="color: #FFFFFF; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; padding: 15px; display: inline-block; background-color: #222;"
        href="<%= url %>">
        Verify Account
    </a>
</body>

</html>